title: OOPSDOGGY Rolled Leather Cat Collar with Bell - Reflective Kitten Collar with Safety Elastic Strap - Adjustable Small Pet Collars for Boy Girl Cats (Burgundy)
features: Adjustable Fit: Suitable for cats with neck sizes ranging from 8" to 11". Please measure your cat's neck with a soft measuring tape to ensure the correct fit. Sizes may vary based on the age and breed of your cat, so accurate measurement is essential.

Soft Rolled Leather: Made from rolled leather, these cat collars with bell are gentle on long hair, helping to prevent matting and tangling, a common issue with traditional collars. Available in 12 vibrant colors. Designed to minimize clawing and chewing, ensuring your pet's comfort and longevity of the collar.
Improved Visibility: Features reflective thread for added visibility, ensuring your cat's safety in low-light conditions.
Safety Release Elastic Strap: The elastic strap is designed to allow easy release if your collar for cats gets snagged on something, ensuring your pet's safety.

Built-in Safety Bell: Enhance your cat's safety with our integrated, removable bell, designed to alert and deter potential prey, offering flexibility based on your preference; this stylish reflective leather cat collar serves as both a fashionable accessory and a practical safety measure for everyday use.
description: Product description Introducing our premium leather cat collar designed with your pet's comfort and safety in mind. It features an adjustable fit suitable for neck sizes ranging from 8" to 11". Made from soft rolled leather, it prevents matting and tangling of long hair and is available in 14 vibrant colors. The small dog collar is designed to minimize clawing and chewing, ensuring durability and comfort. For added safety, it includes reflective thread to enhance visibility in low-light conditions. The safety release elastic strap allows for easy release if the collar becomes snagged, prioritizing your pet's safety. Additionally, a built-in, removable bell enhances security by alerting and deterring potential prey. This stylish leather cat collar combines practicality with aesthetic appeal, making it an ideal choice for everyday use. Directions Everyday Use Directions Dogs
